snippet.title: Dev Diary 01
snippet.description: This is the first video in a series, which delves behind the development process veil. We start with a quick demo of our new Settings panel (work in progress), with a quick discussion of our design process, and other tibits on our dev process (and there is a bit about IKEA in there for good measure...)
